HealthCheckDto.description: Standard health check sent from healthz endpoint and between services.

key.description: Gets or sets unique key name for this health check result, can be used to recreate graph.

description.description: Gets or sets description of the health status.

version.description: Gets or sets assembly version of this component.

entries.description: Gets or sets individual subsystem health states or null if no subsystems.

entriesWithPayload.description: Gets the entries as a dictionary of objects with any additional payload properties like version.
